### Login as admin
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@cmms.com",
  "password": "Admin1234"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.tokens.accessToken)
%}

### Get my notifications
GET http://localhost:3000/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get unread count
GET http://localhost:3000/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Create announcement (wszyscy użytkownicy)
POST http://localhost:3000/notifications/announcement
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Planowana przerwa w dostawie prądu",
  "message": "W dniu 20.04.2026 od 8:00 do 12:00 planowana jest przerwa w dostawie prądu"
}

### Get my notifications (po announcement)
GET http://localhost:3000/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

> {% client.global.set("notificationId", response.body[0].id) %}

### Mark as read
PATCH http://localhost:3000/notifications/{{notificationId}}/read
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Mark all as read
PATCH http://localhost:3000/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get all notifications (admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/notifications/all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Delete notification
DELETE http://localhost:3000/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
